ValaTerm is a lightweight terminal written in Vala.

Build Requirements
==================

 * valac >= 0.10.0 but >= 0.12.1 is better if you using vte >= 0.26
 * gcc or Clang/LLVM
 * intltool
 * gettext
 * pkg-config

Run Requirements
================

 * glib-2.0 >= 2.6
 * gtk+-2.0 >= 2.16
 * vte >= 0.20

